491
00:22:00,895 --> 00:22:02,021
Sa petite ...?

492
00:22:02,095 --> 00:22:03,562
Quoi?

493
00:22:03,627 --> 00:22:05,423
On nous a dit que la petite amie de
Warren travaillait ici.

494
00:22:05,498 --> 00:22:07,090
Eh bien, enfin, si vous aviez
rencontré Warren,

495
00:22:07,167 --> 00:22:09,323
